        in each case without payment to the Licensor, provided they comply with Section 4 (Prohibited Uses).

   3.4. Paid Teaching and Training
        Educators, trainers, and consultants MAY receive payment for their teaching, training, or consulting services while using or demonstrating the Software, as long as they do not provide the Software as a Hosting Service and do not sell the Software itself as a product.

